    <li><span class="stat-n">18 MB</span><span class="stat-l">the entire server, one static file</span></li>
    <li><span class="stat-n">~23 MB</span><span class="stat-l">RAM for a whole running space — app, database, frontend</span></li>
    <li><span class="stat-n">1.3 MB</span><span class="stat-l">the iPhone app download</span></li>
    <li><span class="stat-n">2.2 MB</span><span class="stat-l">the Mac app download</span></li>
    <li><span class="stat-n">0.21</span><span class="stat-l">load average of the whole production fleet on 2 vCPUs</span></li>
  </ul>
